messages.content: I always get the two or five rights, so I said I'm going to get extra meat this time.
But he didn't even, can you get me extra scrim or can you get my money back?
So I just said, I'm going to call the police.
Okay, we'll get somebody out there.
I was trying to get a police officer up here.
I'm going to send an officer. I just don't know how long it's going to take.
